Shungu pamusoro pamachinda aIsiraeri 19Zvino iwe, imba mariro pamu- soro pamachinda aIsiraeri, 2 uti, "Mai vako vaiva aniko?" Vaiva shumbakadzi, yaivata pakati peshumba, ichirera vana vayo pakati peshumba duku. 3 Zvino yakarera mumwe mwana wayo, ikava shumba duku, ikadzidza kubata zvaingauraya, ikapedza vanhu. 4 Marudzi avanhu akainzwawo ikabatwa muhuzha yavo, vakaiisa kunyika yeIjipiti. 5 Zvino yakati ichiona kuti yanyengerwa, kuti tariro yanyangarika, ikatorazve mumwe mwana wayo, ikaiita shumba duku. 6 Iyo ikafamba-famba pakati peshumba; ikava shumba duku, ikadzidza kubata zvaingauraya, ikapedza vanhu. 7 Ikaziva dzimba dzavo dzohushe, ikaparadza maguta avo; nyika nezvose zvayo ikava dongo, nokuda kwokuwomba kwayo. 8 Ipapo marudzi avanhu venyika dzakapoteredza akarwa nayo, vakakandira mumbure wavo pamusoro payo, ikabatwa muhuzha yavo. 9 Vakaiisa muchirugu chine zvikokowono, vakandoiisa kuna mambo weBhabhironi; vakaiisa munhare, kuti izwi rayo rirege kuzonzwika pamakomo alsiraeri. 10 Mai vako vakanga vakaita somudzambiringa, panguva yokuzorora kwako, wakanga wakasimwa pamvura;
\c 19
